data.description: Get ready to be charmed by this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home nestled in Jonesboro! Ideal for first-time buyer, this cozy 4-sided brick Ranch offers a spacious backyard. The garage has been cleverly repurposed into a versatile bonus room that can serve as a 4th bedroom, media room, playroom, or office!   The kitchen, overlooking the dining area, is perfect for hosting gatherings.  While recent updates include fresh paint throughout and updated bathrooms. With no HOA fees and charming hardwood floors, this home is ready to welcome its new owners with warmth and style.  Conveniently situated close to major services and just a short 15-minute drive to I-75, this home offers both comfort and accessibility.
